The market is expected to grow at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2030.

9. What are the benefits of using blue glass bottles over plastic packaging?

Blue glass bottles are more environmentally friendly, recyclable, and provide better product protection than plastic.

10. Is there a demand for blue glass bottles in the pharmaceutical industry?

Yes, blue glass bottles are used in the pharmaceutical industry due to their ability to preserve the integrity of sensitive products.

